item.title: Genesys International likely to bag orders worth INR 200 cr from automakers
item.description: The market for navigation maps and connected car solutions in India is currently valued at about INR 180-200 crore and is projected to reach INR 500-600 crore in the next 3-4 years. Genesys International aims to capture a significant market share in the automotive mapping sector, which is growing rapidly.

item.title: South Korea Battery Maker Arrested Over Factory Fire That Killed 23
item.description: The CEO of a South Korean lithium battery maker has been arrested over a factory fire that killed 23 people in June, a local court told AFP Thursday.
